data.name: deltarice
data.description: A high-performance compression library optimized for up-to 16-bit digitized analog signals

evidence: README install command: "conda install -c anaconda hdf5"

"This is the git repo for the Delta-Rice compression algorithm. ... Delta-Rice contains a Python/C package that implements this algorithm through HDF5. It is loaded via the dynamically loaded filters framework and uses filter ID 32025."

Python example imports and uses it as a library: "import deltaRice.h5" and then passes "compression=deltaRice.h5.H5FILTER" into h5py.create_dataset, indicating it is a reusable compression component rather than a standalone app.
